| Layer          | Technology                                             |
| -------------- | ------------------------------------------------------ |
| Frontend       | React + Vue, TailwindCSS / Material-UI                 |
| Backend        | Node.js + Express                                      |
| Database       | MongoDB                                                |
| Video          | HTML5 / Custom React Player                            |
| Metadata       | MongoDB + TMDb / OMDb API                              |
| Hosting        | Local PC / Home Server                                 |
| Network Access | LAN (and optional port forwarding for external access) |

